query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.stock,
  i.lastRestockDate,
  p.id as productId,
  p.name as productName,
  p.price as productPrice,
  p.stockAlert
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN inventory i ON i.productId = p.id AND i.userId = 1
WHERE p.userId = 1;
